            "pub_date": "2026-04-15 08:46:49",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "藥捷安康折讓18%配股籌2.9億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藥捷安康(02617)公布，擬配售508.5萬股集資約2.9億元；配股價57.03元，較該股昨收市價69.55元折讓18%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"藥捷安康官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/02617-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"藥捷安康官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/02617-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">藥捷安康官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價70.58元比較，今次配股價折讓達19.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">預期今次集資淨額約2.82億元，當中約57%用於研發，包括公司的核心產品Tinengotinib在晚期乳腺癌、肝細胞癌、去勢抵抗性前列腺癌等適應症的臨床開發，以及TT-00973的臨床開發。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外約33%用於核心產品Tinengotinib在中國的生產及其商業化，包括商業團隊的組建及相關營銷活動；約10%用於營運資金及一般企業用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15874217-%e8%97%a5%e6%8d%b7%e5%ae%89%e5%ba%b7%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9318%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c2-9%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250916_FI_source-web_02617.jpg.webp",
