            "title": "黑期夜期齊越26100點高水逾270點 重磅港股ADR全高收京東漲超6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時14分升303點或1.17%，報26188點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報26125點，較香港上日現貨收市高253點或0.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣499.3元，較上日香港收市高6.06元或1.23%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣128.6元，較上日香港收市高4.12元或3.31%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣86.6元，較上日香港收市高1.47元或1.72%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣122.4元，較上日香港收市高7.01元或6.07%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣31.2元，較上日香港收市高0.3元或0.97%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251216_FI_source-web_09618-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251216_FI_source-web_09618-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣143.2元，較上日香港收市高2.16元或1.53%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣88元，較上日香港收市高0.98元或1.12%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣412元，較上日香港收市高4.79元或1.18%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣64元，較上日香港收市高0.72元或1.13%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.5元，較上日香港收市高0.03元或0.33%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報26145點，升229點，較上日恒指收市25872點，高水273點。科指期貨夜市收報4943點，較上日科指收市高水91點；國指期貨夜市收報8761點，較上日國指收市高水89點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15874171-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e9%bd%8a%e8%b6%8a26100%e9%bb%9e%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be270%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%85%a8%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e4%ba%ac%e6%9d%b1",
