        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段續揚 日股暫升逾1% 韓股跑贏漲近3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場繼續憧憬美伊重返談判桌，華爾街股市昨晚再度揚升，推動日韓股市今早初段進一步向上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241030_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241030_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時12分，日經平均指數升606點或1.05%，報58484點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫升172點或2.9%，報6140點。</p>\n</div>",
